Potential issues on the main thread: If a large calculation is performed directly on the main thread, it will block the browser's UI thread. This means the page will become unresponsive: users won't be able to click buttons, scroll, or interact with any elements, and animations will freeze. The browser might even show a 'script unresponsive' warning.

